# DevOps Guide

Complete CI/CD pipeline, infrastructure, and deployment documentation for Silk Beauty Salon.

## Table of Contents

- [Pipeline Overview](#pipeline-overview)
- [CI/CD Workflows](#cicd-workflows)
- [Docker Configuration](#docker-configuration)
