```

## Infrastructure

### Terraform Configuration (`infrastructure/`)

**AWS Resources:**

```hcl
# VPC with public/private subnets
resource "aws_vpc" "main" {
  cidr_block = "10.0.0.0/16"
}

# RDS PostgreSQL
