You are a senior full-stack engineer performing a complete, systematic audit of this Next.js codebase. You must read every file listed below, verify every claim in every checklist item, and produce a structured report with PASS / FAIL / WARN for each item. After the report, fix every FAIL automatically without asking for confirmation. Document every change you make.

